.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gandhi%2C%2077%2C%20will%20not%2C%20however%2C%20withdraw%20from%20public%20life%20just%20yet%3B%20this%20is%20not%20a%20retirement%20but%20a%20repositioning%2C%20of%20sorts.%20She%20will%20move%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20filed%20her%20nomination%20papers%20from%20Rajasthan%20today%20and%20will%20take%20over%20-%20the%20Congress%20has%20the%20numbers%20to%20guarantee%20her%20election%20-%20the%20seat%20now%20held%20by%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20party%20stalwart%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20who%20may%20retire%20after%20a%20celebrated%20five-decade%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsonia-gandhi-files-her-nomination-for-rajya-sabha-from-rajasthan-5055020%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESonia%20Gandhi%20Files%20Her%20Nomination%20For%20Rajya%20Sabha%20From%20Rajasthan%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonia%20Gandhi%20contested%20her%20first%20election%20from%20the%20party%20stronghold%20of%20Amethi%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20from%20Karnataka's%20Bellary.%20She%20won%20both.%20That%20was%20in%201999%2C%20eight%20years%20after%20her%20husband%20and%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20was%20assassinated%2C%20and%20she%20was%20persuaded%20to%20help%20rescue%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202004%20she%20shifted%20to%20the%20Congress'%20second%20UP%20stronghold%20-%20Raebareli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20has%20been%20ever-present%20since%201999%2C%20serving%20as%20a%20steadying%20and%20guiding%20force%20for%20her%20party%2C%20particularly%20through%20the%20political%20and%20parliamentary%20turbulence%20of%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20parliament%20and%20outside%20she%20often%20let%20her%20colleagues%20take%20centre-stage%2C%20but%20the%20normally%20soft-spoken%20Ms%20Gandhi%20was%20capable%20of%20sharp%20attacks%2C%20including%20in%20September%20and%20December%20last%20year%2C%20when%20she%20took%20the%20BJP%20head-on%20over%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20and%20the%20mass%20suspension%20of%20opposition%20MPs%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-lok-sabha-on-womens-bill-sonia-gandhi-kanimozhi-supriya-sule-kakoli-ghosh-lead-charge-smriti-irani-replies-4407051%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOn%20Women's%20Bill%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Kanimozhi%20Lead%20Charge%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%20she%20ripped%20into%20the%20government%2C%20declaring%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20PM%20is%20very%20good%20at%20lectures...%20but%20lectures%20cannot%20fill%20stomachs.%20You%20need%20dal%20chawal.%20Lectures%20don't%20heal%20the%20sick...%20you%20need%20health%20centres.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%202015%20too%20she%20threw%20down%20against%20Mr%20Modi%2C%20this%20time%20arguing%20against%20his%20%26quot%3Bmany%20fraudulent%20promises%20about%20transparency%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20debate%20over%20key%20posts%2C%20like%20Chief%20Information%20Commissioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gandhi's%20position%20as%2C%20perhaps%2C%20the%20foremost%20opposition%20politician%2C%20also%20meant%20she%20was%20frequently%20the%20target%20of%20attacks%2C%20particularly%20given%20her%20Italian%20heritage%2C%20with%20many%2C%20including%20now-ally%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20questioning%20her%20political%20credentials.%20That%20line%20of%20attack%20was%20often%20employed%20by%20the%20BJP%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%2C%20though%2C%20rarely%20fazed%2C%20even%20when%20she%20was%20accused%20of%20%26quot%3Blying%26quot%3B%20by%20a%20union%20minister%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Raebareli%20Years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gandhi%20has%20held%20Raebareli%20since%202004%2C%20never%20polling%20below%2055%20per%20cent.%20She%20won%20the%20seat%20even%20in%202014%20and%202019%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20routed%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20BJP%2C%20and%20held%20it%20even%20when%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20lost%20Amethi.%20And%20leaves%20(very)%20big%20shoes%20to%20fill%20for%20whomever%20the%20Congress%20fields%20from%20here%20in%20the%20April%2FMay%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20that%20will%20be%20is%20unclear%20but%20there%20is%20buzz%20one%20Gandhi%20will%20be%20replaced%20by%20another%2C%20and%20that%20it%20will%20not%20be%20Rahul.%20There%20is%20talk%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fpriyanka-gandhi-vadra%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPriyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20whose%20resemblance%20to%20grandmother%20and%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20has%20been%20noted%20-%20is%20being%20readied%20for%20her%20long-awaited%20electoral%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20Mr%20Singh's%20anticipated%20exit%20and%20Ms%20Gandhi's%20predicted%20transfer%20are%20only%20two-thirds%20of%20this%20story%2C%20which%2C%20if%20completed%20to%20script%2C%20will%20signal%20a%20generational%20change%20in%20the%20Congress'%20top%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPriyanka%20Gandhi's%20Entrance%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20always%20been%20a%20'will%20she%2C%20won't%20she'%20air%20about%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra's%20political%20career.%20And%20that%20has%20gathered%20pace%20over%20the%20past%20months%2C%20particularly%20since%20her%20mother%20stepped%20into%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20years%20ago%20-%20before%20the%202019%20election%20-%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20said%20she%20was%20ready%20to%20make%20her%20electoral%20debut%20at%20any%20time%2C%20and%20set%20tongues%20wagging%20after%20quipping%20%26quot%3Bwhy%20not%26quot%3B%20when%20asked%20if%20she%20would%20contest%20from%20UP's%20Varanasi%2C%20a%20contest%20that%20could%20pitch%20her%20into%20a%20head-to-head%20with%20Mr%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3