es-kill-three-injure-13-in-east-ukraine%2Farticleshow%2F107688240.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussias-airstrikes-kill-three-injure-13-in-east-ukraine%2Famp_articleshow%2F107688240.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussias-airstrikes-kill-three-injure-13-in-east-ukraine%2Famp_articleshow%2F107688240.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWorld%20Today%20Needs%20Clean%2C%20Transparent%2C%20Tech-Savvy%20Governments%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%20In%20UAE%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20addressing%20at%20the%20World%20Government%20Summit%20in%20Dubai%2C%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20clean%20and%20transparent%20governance%20as%20a%20crucial%20factor%20in%20addressing%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20governments%20worldwide.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20address%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20also%20acknowledged%20the%20dynamic%20leadership%20of%20UAE%20President%20Sheikh%20Mohammed%20Bin%20Zayed%2C%20describing%20him%20as%20a%20leader%20with%20vision%20and%20resolve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20the%20world%20needs%20a%20smart%20government%2C%20which%20makes%20technology%20a%20government%20medium%2C%20which%20is%20transparent%20and%20not%20corrupt%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%C2%A0%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20world%20is%20embracing%20modernity%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20challenges%20emanating%20since%20the%20last%20century%20are%20on%20a%20continuous%20rise.%20Be%20it%20food%20security%2C%20health%20security%2C%20water%20security%2C%20energy%20security%2C%20education%20or%20building%20an%20inclusive%20society%2C%20every%20government%20is%20bound%20by%20many%20responsibilities%20towards%20its%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE)%20marks%20his%20seventh%20since%202015.%20During%20this%20two-day%20visit%2C%20he%20is%20expected%20to%20engage%20in%20wide-ranging%20talks%20with%20top%20leaders%20of%20the%20UAE%20to%20further%20strengthen%20the%20existing%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20highlights%20of%20the%20visit%20is%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20BAPS%20Mandir%2C%20the%20first%20Hindu%20temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20later%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UAE%20was%20one%20of%20the%20top%20four%20foreign%20direct%20investors%20in%20India%20during%20the%20fiscal%20year%202022-23.%20Bilateral%20trade%20between%20India%20and%20the%20UAE%20reached%20an%20impressive%20%2485%20billion%20during%20that%20time%2C%20solidifying%20their%20positions%20as%20crucial%20trading%20partners%20for%20each%20other.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20economic%20collaboration%20has%20been%20further%20facilitated%20by%20agreements%20such%20as%20the%20Comprehensive%20Economic%20Partnership%20Agreement%20(CEPA)%20signed%20in%20February%202022%20and%20the%20Local%20Currency%20Settlement%20(LCS)%20System%20established%20in%20July%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20community%2C%20numbering%20around%203.5%20million%20in%20the%20UAE%2C%20forms%20the%20largest%20expatriate%20group%20in%20the%20country.%20Their%20contributions%20to%20the%20socio-economic%20development%20of%20the%20UAE%20have%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20fostering%20strong%20people-to-people%20ties.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707902460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fh5q334ok_modi-in-uae_625x300_14_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworld-today-needs-clean-transparent-tech-savvy-governments-pm-modi-in-uae-5055642%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20addressing%20at%20the%20World%20Government%20Summit%20in%20Dubai%2C%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20clean%20and%20transparent%20governance%20as%20a%20crucial%20factor%20in%20addressing%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20governments%20worldwide.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworld-today-needs-clean-transparent-tech-savvy-governments-pm-modi-in-uae-5055642%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworld-today-needs-clean-transparent-tech-savvy-governments-pm-modi-in-uae-5055642%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworld-today-needs-clean-transparent-tech-savvy-governments-pm-modi-in-uae-5055642%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Family%20Found%20Dead%20With%20Gunshot%20Wounds%20At%20Their%20%242%20Million%20US%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20Indian-origin%20family%20from%20Kerala%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20their%20home%20in%20US'%20California%20in%20an%20apparent%20case%20of%20murder-suicide.%20The%20family%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Anand%20Sujith%20Henry%2C%2042%2C%20his%20wife%20Alice%20Priyanka%2C%2040%2C%20and%20their%204-year-old%20twin%20children%20Noah%20and%20Neithan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECops%20found%20the%20bodies%20after%20one%20of%20the%20family's%20relatives%20sought%20a%20welfare%20check%20as%20nobody%20in%20the%20house%20was%20attending%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian-American%20couple%2C%20Anand%20and%20Alice%2C%20were%20found%20dead%20with%20gunshot%20wounds%20inside%20a%20bathroom.%20The%20twin%20children%20were%20discovered%20dead%20in%20a%20bedroom%2C%20with%20the%20cause%20of%20their%20death%20still%20under%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20arriving%20officers%20were%20met%20with%20no%20response%2C%20they%20searched%20the%20perimeter%20of%20the%20home%20and%20did%20not%20see%20any%20signs%20of%20forced%20entry%20into%20the%20house.%20Finding%20an%20unlocked%20window%2C%20officers%20entered%20the%20home%20and%20located%20four%20people%20dead%3B%201%20adult%20male%2C%201%20adult%20female%2C%20and%20two%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%209mm%20pistol%20and%20a%20loaded%20magazine%20were%20recovered%20from%20the%20bathroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20had%20purchased%20the%20house%20in%202020%20for%20%242.1%20million%2C%20records%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20initial%20assessment%20by%20the%20police%20suggests%20a%20possible%20murder-suicide%20scenario%2C%20though%20they%20have%20not%20ruled%20out%20other%20possibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20the%20information%20we%20have%20at%20this%20time%2C%20this%20appears%20to%20be%20an%20isolated%20incident%20with%20no%20danger%20to%20the%20public%20as%20we%20are%20confident%20the%20person%20responsible%20was%20located%20within%20the%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20San%20Mateo%20police%20department%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%2C%20originally%20from%20Kerala%2C%20had%20been%20living%20in%20the%20United%20States%20for%20the%20past%20nine%20years.%20Anand%2C%20a%20software%20engineer%2C%20and%20Alice%2C%20a%20senior%20analyst%2C%20had%20relocated%20from%20New%20Jersey%20to%20San%20Mateo%20County%20two%20years%20ago.%20Described%20as%20friendly%2C%20hardworking%2C%20and%20devoted%20parents%2C%20the%20couple%20was%20well-liked%20by%20both%20neighbors%20and%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20court%20records%2C%20Anand%20had%20filed%20for%20divorce%20in%20December%202016%2C%20but%20the%20separation%20did%20not%20go%20through%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESan%20Mateo%20County's%20Criminal%20Investigation%20Bureau%20(CIB)%20has%20taken%20over%20the%20case%2C%20working%20alongside%20the%20San%20Mateo%20County%20Crime%20Lab%20to%20collect%20evidence.%20The%20bodies%20have%20been%20taken%20into%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20San%20Mateo%20County%20Coroner%2C%20who%20is%20working%20to%20positively%20identify%20each%20individual%20and%20notify%20next%20of%20kin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20bears%20an%20eerie%20resemblance%20to%20a%20recent%20case%20where%20a%20wealthy%20Indian-origin%20couple%20and%20their%20teenage%20daughter%20were%20found%20dead%20in%20their%20%245%20million%20mansion%20in%20Massachusetts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20month%2C%20at%20least%20seven%20Indian-origin%20people%20have%20been%20found%20dead%20in%20the%20US.%20US%20envoy%20to%20India%20Eric%20Garcetti%20reassured%20that%20the%20US%20is%20committed%20to%20making%20sure%20it%20remains%20a%20safe%20destination%20for%20Indian%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707902340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fmgn5sqas_indian-family_625x300_14_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-american-couple-twin-sons-found-dead-at-their-home-in-california-5055481%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Indian-origin%20family%20from%20Kerala%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20their%20home%20in%20US'%20California%20in%20an%20apparent%20case%20of%20murder-suicide.%20The%20victims%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Anand%20Sujith%20Henry%2C%2042%2C%20his%20wife%20Alice%20Priyanka%2C%2040%2C%20and%20their%204-year-old%20twin%20children.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-american-couple-twin-sons-found-dead-at-their-home-in-california-5055481%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-american-couple-twin-sons-found-dead-at-their-home-in-california-5055481%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-american-couple-twin-sons-found-dead-at-their-home-in-california-5055481%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Better%20than%20roses%3A%20Thai%20couples%20marry%20on%20elephants%20f