There%20has%20been%20a%20change%20in%20circumstances%2C%20we%20will%20try%20our%20luck%20in%20the%20trial%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20Khalid%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20Kapil%20Sibal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fumar-khalid-withdraws-bail-petition-in-supreme-court-to-seek-bail-from-trial-court-afresh-249452%5C%22%3Ewas%20quoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20saying%20to%20the%20court%20by%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Bela%20Trivedi%20and%20Pankaj%20Mithal%20dismissed%20Khalid%E2%80%99s%20petition%20as%20withdrawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20elaborating%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cchange%20in%20circumstances%E2%80%9D%2C%20Khalid%E2%80%99s%20father%20S.Q.R.%20Ilyas%2C%20while%20speaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20cited%20the%20long%20adjournments%20in%20the%20bail%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20May%202023%2C%20there%20have%20been%20several%20adjournments.%20We%20were%20assessing%20that%20this%20is%20a%20lengthy%20procedure%20and%20the%20circumstances%20have%20changed.%20So%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20move%20the%20trial%20court%20again%2C%20and%20hope%20for%20an%20early%20judgment.%20So%20we%20will%20try%20our%20luck%20there%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhalid%20was%20arrested%20in%20September%202020%2C%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20case%20related%20to%20the%20North-East%20Delhi%20communal%20violence%20that%20erupted%20in%20February%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20the%20submission%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20while%20the%20bench%20was%20hearing%20his%20special%20leave%20petition%2C%20challenging%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20deny%20him%20bail%20in%20October%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.knightlab.com%2Flibs%2Ftimeline3%2Flatest%2Fembed%2Findex.html%3Fsource%3D1qjbCTSktnqwFmsmLOkelAHTPhgM8Nrf-hEfysCB8lKw%26font%3DDefault%26lang%3Den%26initial_zoom%3D2%26height%3D650%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20bench%2C%20comprising%20Justices%20Sidharth%20Mridul%20and%20Rajnesh%20Bhatnagar%2C%20while%20rejecting%20his%20bail%20plea%2C%20had%20held%20that%20the%20prosecution%E2%80%99s%20case%20and%20the%20chargesheet%20make%20for%20a%20prima%20facie%20case%20against%20Khalid%2C%20who%20is%20accused%20of%20criminal%20conspiracy%20under%20the%20UAPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESibal%20told%20the%20court%20that%20he%20will%20argue%20the%20separate%20writ%20petition%20filed%20by%20Khalid%20challenging%20the%20constitutionality%20of%20the%20UAPA%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fpolice-witness-not-credible-callous-probe-how-the-delhi-riots-cases-have-evolved%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Witness%20May%20Have%20Been%20Tutored%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Callous%20Probe%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20the%202020%20Delhi%20Riots%20Cases%20Have%20Evolved%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhalid%2C%20who%20has%20been%20lodged%20in%20jail%20since%20September%2014%2C%202020%2C%20has%20been%20incarcerated%20without%20any%20substantive%20bail%20hearings.%20Along%20with%20UAPA%2C%20he%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20sedition%20and%2018%20other%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20including%20murder%20and%20attempt%20to%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20months%20after%20his%20arrest%2C%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20took%20cognizance%20of%20the%20chargesheet%20filed%20against%20him%20under%20FIR59%2F2020%2C%20along%20with%20JNU%20scholar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsharjeel-imam-jail-uapa-activist-civil-society-support%5C%22%3ESharjeel%20Imam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20is%20accused%20of%20conspiring%20and%20instigating%20the%20riots%20that%20took%20place%20in%20February%20that%20year%20in%20Northeast%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20October%202020%2C%20Khalid%20was%20also%20charged%20under%20FIR%20101%2F2020%20that%20related%20to%20vandalism%20and%20arson%20during%20the%20riots%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fumar-khalid-delhi-court-khajuri-khas-riots-aarogya-setu%5C%22%3EKhajuri%20Khas%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202021%2C%20Khalid%20was%20granted%20bail%20by%20a%20sessions%20court%20in%20Delhi%2C%20filed%20under%20FIR%20101%2F2020%2C%20but%20continued%20to%20be%20incarcerated%20due%20to%20the%20charges%20against%20him%20under%20FIR%2059%2F2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20FIR%2059%2F2020%2C%20Khalid%20has%20been%20charged%20for%20various%20offences%2C%20including%20rioting%2C%20murder%20and%20unlawful%20assembly%20as%20well%20as%20sections%20of%20the%20UAPA%20and%20the%20Arms%20Act%2C%201959.%20He%20is%20also%20facing%20charges%20under%20sedition%2C%20and%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20eight%20months%20of%20hearings%2C%20in%20March%202022%2C%20a%20Delhi%20sessions%20court%20denied%20him%20bail.%20Khalid%20appealed%20this%20decision%20in%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20the%20following%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20subsequently%20ordered%20that%20the%20bail%20plea%20be%20heard%20regularly%20from%20May%2023%2C%20so%20that%20the%20hearings%20close%20before%20the%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20breaks%20for%20summer%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hearings%20were%20then%20adjourned%20on%20June%204%2C%202022%2C%20as%20the%20court%20went%20for%20summer%20vacation%20till%20July%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2018%2C%202022%2C%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20rejected%20his%20bail%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20month%20later%2C%20on%20November%2018%2C%20Khalid%20moved%20the%20Karkardooma%20court%20seeking%20a%20two-week%20interim%20bail%20to%20attend%20his%20sister%E2%80%99s%20marriage%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%203%2C%202022%20the%20Karkardooma%20court%20acquitted%20Khalid%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98stone%20pelting%E2%80%99%20case%20related%20to%20the%20Delhi%20riots%2C%20but%20continued%20to%20detain%20him%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98larger%20conspiracy%E2%80%99%20around%20the%20riots.%20On%20December%2012%20of%20that%20year%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-umar-khalid-granted-interim-bail-to-attend-sisters-wedding%5C%22%3Ewas%20granted%3C%2Fa%3E%20interim%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fumar-khalid-the-historian-his-continued-imprisonment-is-a-loss-to-the-academic-world%5C%22%3EUmar%20Khalid%2C%20the%20Historian%3A%20His%20Continued%20Imprisonment%20Is%20a%20Loss%20to%20the%20Academic%20World%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%206%2C%202023%2C%20Khalid%20filed%20a%20Special%20Leave%20Petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20appealing%20against%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20October%202022%20order%2C%20denying%20him%20bail%2C%20which%20he%20has%20now%20withdrawn%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2018%2C%202023%2C%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%2C%20comprising%20Justices%20A.S.%20Bopanna%20and%20Hima%20Kohli%2C%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20sought%20a%20response%20to%20Khalid%E2%80%99s%20petition%20within%20six%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20since%20then%20Khalid%E2%80%99s%20bail%20plea%20has%20been%20rescheduled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scobserver.in%2Fjournal%2Fumar-khalid-bail-application-tracker%2F%5C%22%3E14%3C%2Fa%3E%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707901886000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F18112637%2FUmar-Khalid.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fumar-khalid-withdraws-bail-plea-in-supreme-court-citing-change-of-circumstances%22%2C%22summary%22%3A