hu%20border.%20As%20per%20reports%2C%20over%20100%20farmers%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESocial%20media%20accounts%20withheld%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EX%20accounts%20and%20Facebook%20pages%20of%20prominent%20farmer%20leaders%20like%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%2C%20the%20coordinator%20of%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20(KMM)%2C%20Tejveer%20Singh%20Ambala%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20BKU%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%2C%20farmer%20leader%20Ramandeep%20Singh%20Mann%2C%20Surjit%20Singh%20Phull%20from%20BKU%20Krantikari%2C%20farmer%20leader%20Harpal%20Sangha%2C%20Ashok%20Danoda%20from%20Haryana%20and%20many%20others%20have%20been%20withheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20banned%20official%20pages%20which%20supported%20the%20movement%20and%20posted%20updates%20on%20it%2C%20like%20%40Tractor2twitr_P%20run%20by%20Bhavjit%20Singh%2C%20Bhartiya%20Kisan%20Union%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%20and%20Progressive%20Farmers%20Front%2C%20run%20by%20Guramneet%20Singh%20Mangat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBKU%20(SBS)%20is%20one%20of%20the%20main%20farmer%20unions%20which%20was%20leading%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20from%20Ambala%2C%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Gaon%20Sawera%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20page%20run%20by%20independent%20journalist%20Mandeep%20Punia%20has%20been%20withheld%2C%20as%20has%20been%20Mandeep%E2%80%99s%20personal%20page.%20Mandeep%20is%20a%20prominent%20name%20supporting%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20and%20had%20been%20arrested%20in%202020.%20In%20the%20jail%2C%20Mandeep%20took%20notes%20on%20his%20legs%20and%20then%20wrote%20a%20report%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Caravan.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20withholding%20these%20accounts%20has%20been%20largely%20understood%20to%20be%20opaque.%20Guramneet%E2%80%99s%20personal%20X%20account%20is%20still%20up%2C%20as%20is%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%E2%80%99s%20X%20account.%20But%20Dallewal%E2%80%99s%20Facebook%20page%20is%20banned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accounts%20received%20a%20message%20from%20X%20saying%3A%20%E2%80%9CYour%20account%20has%20been%20withheld%20in%20IN%20%5BIndia%5D%20in%20response%20to%20a%20legal%20demand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20official%20page%20of%20Kisan%20Majdoor%20Morcha%2C%20which%20was%20started%20recently%20ahead%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20protest%2C%20is%20still%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20pertinent%20to%20mention%20here%20that%20earlier%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20in%202020-2021%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20banned%20many%20social%20media%20accounts%20including%20the%20official%20page%20of%20Kisan%20Ekta%20Morcha%2C%20which%20largely%20functioned%20as%20the%20digital%20outpost%20of%20the%20SKM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20then%20high%20profile%20supporters%20like%20Punjabi%20singer%20Jazzy%20B%20and%20Khalsa%20Aid%E2%80%99s%20Ravi%20Singh%2C%20along%20with%20independent%20journalist%20Sandeep%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20accounts%20had%20been%20withheld%20and%20continue%20to%20be%20under%20lock%20and%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccounts%20meant%20to%20debunk%20propaganda%20targeted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Bhavjit%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20running%20the%20%40Tractor2Twitr_i%20page%20on%20X%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20withheld%20in%20the%20time%20between%20he%20spoke%20and%20this%20report%20was%20published%20%E2%80%93%20said%20that%20all%20these%20accounts%20were%20withheld%20as%20farmer%20leaders%20were%20sitting%20at%20a%20meeting%20with%20union%20ministers%20on%20February%2012.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20an%20assumption%20that%20it%20is%20not%20just%20the%20Union%20government%20but%20the%20Punjab%20government%20too%20which%20was%20involved%20in%20singling%20out%20farmer%20union%20leaders%E2%80%99%20accounts.%20This%20is%20a%20dangerous%20trend%2C%20as%20those%20accounts%20which%20were%20running%20propaganda%20against%20farmers%20are%20getting%20sup