pressure%20on%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fact%20is%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20afraid%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20strength%2C%20which%20they%20have%20already%20seen%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20in%202020.%20Let%20them%20try%20whatever%20they%20want%20to%2C%20farmers%20are%20united%20and%20committed%20to%20their%20cause%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20spoke%20to%20Harinder%20Happy%2C%20a%20PhD%20student%20from%20JawaharLal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20Delhi%20who%2C%20among%20others%2C%20was%20running%20the%20Kisan%20Ekta%20Morcha%2C%20the%20official%20Twitter%20page%20of%20the%20SKM%20last%20time.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20resorted%20to%20these%20tactics%20last%20time%20too%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20two%20years%20since%20they%20banned%20the%20Kisan%20Ekta%20Morcha%20page%2C%20which%20had%20over%20five%20lakh%20followers.%20Our%20page%20was%20withheld%20when%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20was%20at%20its%20peak.%20However%2C%20this%20time%20considering%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%202024%20and%20the%20mass%20support%20for%20farmers%2C%20they%20withheld%20the%20X%20accounts%20on%20the%20very%20first%20day%20of%20the%20protest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHappy%20highlighted%20how%20%E2%80%9Con%20one%20hand%2C%20BJP%20is%20giving%20Bharat%20Ratna%20to%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20and%20M.S.%20Swaminathan%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20they%20were%20not%20implementing%20their%20findings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707901810000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14132746%2FUntitled-design-7-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-social-media-accounts-withheld-protest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bhavjit%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20now%20running%20the%20%40Tractor2Tw