y%20being%20reviewed%20by%20a%20panel%20led%20by%20former%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind.%20Mr%20Stalin%20said%20the%20plan%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bthreat%20to%20democratic%20decentralisation%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20impractical%2C%20not%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%20Elections%20to%20local%20bodies%2C%20state%20assemblies%20and%20parliament%20are%20being%20held%20at%20different%20times%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20people-centric%20issues%20in%20a%20vast%20and%20diverse%20country%20like%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDMK%20allies%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20supported%20the%20resolution.%20Leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20Legislature%20Party%2C%20K%20Selvaperunthagai%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20lie%20that%20elections%20cost%20a%20lot.%20It's%20less%20than%201%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20country's%20budget%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AIADMK%2C%20which%20recently%20snapped%20ties%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20offered%20conditional%20support%20to%20the%20'One%20Nation%20One%20Election'%20plan.%20The%20main%20Opposition%20party%20backed%20the%20resolution%20against%20the%20delimitation%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MLA%20Vanathi%20Srinivasan%20backed%20the%20resolution%20against%20delimitation%20but%20opposed%20the%20one%20challenging%20the%20'One%20Nation%20One%20Election'%20proposal.%20She%20said%20it's%20a%20poll%20reform%20aimed%20at%20seamless%20implementation%20of%20welfare%20schemes%20that%20are%20hampered%20by%20the%20poll%20code%20ahead%20of%20state%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707901800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fi1j6ar84_mk-stalin-1200_625x300_29_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftamil-nadu-assembly-mk-stalin-in-tamil-nadu-assembly-a-challenge-to-delimitation-one-nation-one-poll-5055637%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20first%20by%20any%20state%20legislature%2C%20the%20Tamil%20