untry%20may%20need%20another%20national%20vote%20before%20too%20long%20to%20secure%20a%20more%20stable%20and%20workable%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20election%20has%20been%20called%20flawed%20in%20the%20West.%20Is%20that%20fair%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20standards%2C%20the%20actual%20polling%20went%20off%20relatively%20peacefully.%20There%20was%20a%20terrible%20attack%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.france24.com%2Fen%2Flive-news%2F20240118-baluchistan-explosive-region-on-iran-pakistan-borderland%5C%22%3Erestive%20province%20of%20Baluchistan%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20election%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68226516%5C%22%3Ekilled%2028%20people%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20fears%20of%20widespread%20violence%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20election%20did%20not%20materialise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20there%20were%20undue%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fpakistan-election-human-rights-commission-khan-3258e2131ac83e89c2c376b476caccec%5C%22%3Ecurbs%20on%20political%20activity%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apstylebook.com%2Fsearch%3Fquery%3Drunup%26button%3D%5C%22%3Erun-up%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20election%20itself%20appears%20to%20be%20largely%20credible%20by%20Pakistani%20standards%2C%20as%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20ministry%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usnews.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Farticles%2F2024-02-10%2Fpakistan-hits-back-at-criticism-of-election-conduct-and-insists-cellphone-curbs-were-necessary%5C%22%3Equick%20to%20attest%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20the%20PTI%2C%20a%20party%20that%20is%20out%20of%20favour%20with%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20current%20senior%20military%20leadership%2C%20has%20done%20so%20well%20suggests%20there%20was%20no%20straightforward%20rigging%20across%20the%20board.%20There%20was%20harassment%20of%20PTI%20voters%20in%20some%20places%2C%20but%20it%20clearly%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20sufficient%20to%20make%20huge%20inroads%20into%20their%20overall%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20can%E2%80%99t%20compare%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20democracy%20with%20that%20of%20the%20U.S.%20or%20any%20other%20country.%20The%20problem%20with%20many%20outside%20observers%20of%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20politics%20is%20that%20they%20talk%20normatively%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%2C%20they%20see%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20elections%20through%20the%20eyes%20of%20what%20is%20generally%20seen%20as%20the%20norm%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Pakistani%20politics%20are%20unique.%20The%20country%20is%20a%20military-dominated%20state%2C%20with%20generals%20that%20have%20long%20been%20involved%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F02%2F04%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fpakistan-election-imran-khan.html%5C%22%3Eand%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20alternative%20to%20managed%20elections%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20messy%2C%20is%20martial%20law.%20And%20a%20flawed%20democracy%20is%20better%20than%20the%20military%20jackboot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20that%2C%20the%20election%20itself%20took%20place%20relatively%20peacefully.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20criticism%20in%20the%20West%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F2%2F8%2Finherently-undemocratic-pakistan-suspends-mobile-services-on-voting-day%5C%22%3Ecellphones%20and%20mobile%20internet%20services%20being%20blocked%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20election%20day.%20That%20may%20seem%20like%20unacceptable%20interference%20in%20the%20electoral%20process%20to%20outside%20observers.%20But%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20there%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrance24.com%2Fen%2F20121123-pakistan-suspends-mobile-phone-service-security-ashura-shiite-terrorism%5C%22%3Ereal%20concern%20about%20cellphones%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20used%20to%20detonate%20explosive%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20anyone%20be%20pleased%20with%20the%20election%20result%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20while%20the%20PTI%E2%80%99s%20strong%20showing%20represents%20an%20anti-establishment%20vote%20%E2%80%93%20and%2C%20more%20specifically%2C%20an%20anti-army%20vote%20%E2%80%93%20the%20divided%20national%20mandate%20means%20the%20army%20high%20command%20has%20reason%20to%20be%20satisfied%20with%20the%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20split%20national%20assembly%20and%20weak%20government%20plays%20into%20the%20military%E2%80%99s%20hands.%20Should%20the%20PMLN%20govern%20as%20the%20major%20party%20in%20a%20coalition%2C%20it%20will%20be%20in%20a%20position%20of%20relative%20weakness%20and%20will%20need%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20PTI%20engages%20in%20widespread%20protests%20against%20the%20election%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20there%20any%20positives%20from%20the%20election%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20insofar%20as%20the%20process%20of%20seeking%20the%20peoples%E2%80%99%20support%20has%20been%20allowed%20to%20continue.%20But%20the%20negatives%20are%20seen%20by%20most%20to%20outweigh%20the%20positives%20and%20the%202024%20elections%20are%20being%20viewed%20as%20equally%20%E2%80%93%20if%20not%20more%20%E2%80%93%20manipulated%20and%20controlled%20than%20the%202018%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20turnout%20this%20time%20around%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nation.com.pk%2F10-Feb-2024%2Fvoters-turnout-remain-48-percent-in-election-fafen-report%5C%22%3Eestimated%20to%20be%20around%2048%25%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20lower%20than%20in%202018%20when%20it%20was%2051%25.%20The%20demographic%20breakdown%20is%20encouraging.%20The%20youth%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%3B%2044%25%20of%20voters%20were%20under%20the%20age%20of%2035.%20And%20women%2C%20too%2C%20played%20a%20larger%20role%20in%20the%20vote%20%E2%80%93%20more%20women%20contested%20and%20also%20won%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20party%20politics%20aside%2C%20the%20result%20suggests%20that%20old%20tactics%20to%20intimidate%20and%20suppress%20voters%20largely%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work.%20The%20expectation%20was%20that%20the%20spate%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fmain-criminal-cases-against-pakistans-imran-khan-2024-01-31%2F%5C%22%3Elegal%20verdicts%20against%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20weeks%20before%20the%20election%20and%20his%20continued%20imprisonment%20might%20curb%20his%20popularity%20and%20mean%20PTI%20supporters%20would%20stay%20home.%20That%20clearly%20didn%E2%80%99t%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20they%20helped%20deliver%20may%20only%20help%20continue%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20political%20malaise%20as%20it%20heads%20into%20a%20new%2C%20uncertain%20period.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F223287%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAyesha%20Jalal%2C%20Professor%20of%20History%2C%20Tufts%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20licence.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fpakistans-post-election-crisis-how-anti-army-vote-may-deliver-an-unstable-government-that-falls-into-the-militarys-hands-223287%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707896582000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14131050%2FScreenshot-2024-02-14-at-1.10.42%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistans-anti-army-vote%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20result%20suggests%20that%20old%20tactics%20to%20intimidate%20and%20suppress%20voters%20largely%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work.%20But%20Pakistan's%20malaise%20is%20likely%20to%20continue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistans-anti-army-vote%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Names%20of%20%E2%80%98Indira%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Nargis%E2%80%99%20Dropped%20From%20National%20Film%20Awards%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14130752%2Fimage-1827.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20%E2%80%98Indira%20Gandhi%20Award%20for%20Best%20Debut%20Film%20of%20a%20Director%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98Nargis%20Dutt%20Award%20for%20Best%20Feature%20Film%20on%20National%20Integration%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20are%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Film%20Awards%2C%20have%20been%20renamed%20on%20the%20recommendation%20of%20the%20Committee%20for%20Rationalisation%20of%20Film%20Awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fentertainment%2Findira-and-nargis-dropped-from-names-of-top-film-awards%2Farticle67842363.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520%2527Indira%2520Gandhi%2520Award%2520for%2Cfor%2520Rationalization%2520of%2520Film%2520Awards.%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20committee%20recommended%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98Indira%20Gandhi%20Award%20for%20Best%20Debut%20Film%20of%20a%20Director%E2%80%99%20be%20renamed%20as%20%E2%80%98Best%20Debut%20Film%20of%20a%20Director%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20the%20award%20money%20be%20increased%20to%20Rs%203%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20recommended%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98Nargis%20Dutt%20Award%20for%20Best%20Feature%20Film%20on%20National%20Integration%E2%80%99%20be%20renamed%20as%20%E2%80%98Best%20Feature%20Film%20Promoting%20National%2C%20Social%20and%20Environmental%20Values%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20award%20carries%20a%20Rajat%20Kamal%20to%20the%20director%20and%20the%20producer%20with%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20each.%20The%20committee%20recommended%20that%20it%20be%20clubbed%20with%20%E2%80%98Best%20Film%20on%20Social%20Issues%20and%20Best%20Film%20on%20Environment%20Conservation%2FPreservation%E2%80%99.%20The%20award%20amount%20has%20been%20increased%20to%20Rs%202%20lakh%20each%20to%20the%20director%20and%20producer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dadasaheb%20Phalke%20Award%20has%20increased%20from%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20to%20Rs%2015%20lakh%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rationalisation%20committee%20was%20headed%20by%20Neerja%20Sekhar%2C%20additional%20secretary%20in%20the%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20ministry.%20It%20included%20filmmakers%20Priyadarshan%2C%20Vipul%20Shah%2C%20Haobam%20Paban%20Kumar%2C%20Central%20Board%20of%20Film%20Certification%20(CBFC)%20chief%20Prasoon%20Joshi%2C%20cinematographer%20S%20Nallamuthu%20as%20well%20as%20I%26amp%3BB%20joint%20secretary%20Prithul%20Kumar%20and%20the%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20director%20(finance)%20Kamlesh%20Kumar%20Sinha%2C%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fentertainment%2Fnational-film-awards-indira-gandhi-nargis-dutt-names-dropped-from-categories-other-changes-9159306%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20committee%20deliberated%20on%20the%20changes%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20The%20decision%20to%20make%20these%20changes%20was%20ultimately%20unanimous%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20member%20of%20the%20committee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fentertainment%2Fnational-film-awards-indira-gandhi-nargis-dutt-names-dropped-from-categories-other-changes-9159306%2F%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20PTI%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20changes%20include%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20new%20category%20called%20%E2%80%98Best%20AVGC%20Film%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20combines%20the%20Best%20Animation%20Film%20and%20Best%20Special%20Effects%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAwards%20for%20Best%20Actor%2C%20Actress%2C%20Supporting%20Actor%2C%20and%20Supporting%20Actress%20have%20been%20renamed%20and%20the%20prize%20money%20increased.%20Additionally%2C%20changes%20have%20been%20made%20to%20categories%20such%20as%20Best%20Audiography%20and%20Best%20Music%20Director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Best%20Actor%20award%20(Rajat%20Kamal%20with%20Rs%2050%2C000)%20has%20been%20renamed%20as%20%E2%80%98Best%20Actor%20in%20a%20Leading%20Role%E2%80%99%20(Rajat%20Kamal%20and%20Rs%202%20lakh)%3B%20and%20the%20Best%20Actress%20(Rajat%20Kamal%20with%20Rs%2050%2C000)%20to%20%E2%80%98Best%20Actress%20in%20a%20Leading%20Role%E2%80%99%20(Rajat%20Kamal%20with%20Rs%202%20lakh).%20As%20recommended%2C%20the%20Best%20Supporting%20Actor%20award%20(Rajat%20Kamal%20with%20Rs%2050%2C000)%20has%20been%20titled%20%E2%80%98Best%20Actor%20in%20Supporting%20Role%E2%80%99%20(Rajat%20Kamal%20with%20Rs%202%20lakh)%20and%20the%20Best%20Supporting%20Actress%20award%20to%20%E2%80%98Best%20Actress%20in%20a%20Supporting%20Role%E2%80%99%20(Rajat%20Kamal%20with%20Rs%202%20lakh)%2C%20the%20daily%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Best%20Audiography%20category%2C%20the%20three%20sub-categoriesn%20%E2%80%93%20Location%20Sync%20Sound%20Recordist%20(for%20sync%20sound%20only)%2C%20Sound%20Designer%2C%20and%20Recordist%20of%20the%20Final%20Mixed%20Track%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20combined%20and%20rebranded%20as%20%E2%80%98Best%20Sound%20Design%E2%80%99%20(with%20a%20Rajat%20Kamal%20award%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20for%20the%20sound%20designer).%20Similarly%2C%20the%20sub-categories%20of%20Best%20Music%20Director%20(Background%20Music)%20and%20Best%20Music%20Director%20(Background%20Score)%20have%20been%20merged%20into%20%E2%80%98Music%20Director%20(Background%20Music)%E2%80%98%20(with%20a%20Rajat%20Kamal%20award%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20award%20for%20%E2%80%98Best%20Feature%20Film%20in%20each%20of%20the%20language%20specified%20in%20the%20Schedule%20VIII%20of%20the%20Constitution%E2%80%99%20has%20been%20renamed%20as%20%E2%80%98Best%20(name%20of%20the%20language)%20Feature%20Film%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20the%20award%20money%20doubled%20to%20Rs%202%20lakh%20each.%20Similar%20changes%20have%20been%20made%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Feature%20Film%20in%20each%20of%20the%20languages%20other%20than%20those%20specified%20in%20Schedule%20VIII%20of%20the%20Constitution%E2%80%99%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20recommended%20giving%20only%20one%20award%20per%20category%2C%20with%20shared%20awards%20given%20only%20under%20exceptional%20circumstances%20to%20maintain%20the%20prestige%20of%20the%20awards.%20Uniform%20cash%20awards%20have%20been%20set%20at%20Rs%203%20lakh%20for%20Swarna%20Kamal%20winners%20and%20Rs%202%20lakh%20for%20Rajat%20Kamal%20winners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2070th%20edition%20of%20the%20awards%20will%20be%20held%20this%20year.%20The%20entries%20for%20this%20edition%20were%20sought%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707896522000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14130752%2Fimage-1827.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnames-of-indira-and-nargis-dropped-from-national-film-awards%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20%E2%80%98Indira%20Gandhi%20Award%20for%20Best%20Debut%20Film%20of%20a%20Director%E2%80%99%20has%20been%20renamed%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Best%20Debut%20Film%20of%20a%20Director'.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Nargis%20Dutt%20Award%20for%20Best%20Feature%20Film%20on%20National%20Integration%E2%80%99%20will%20now%20be%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98Best%20Feature%20Film%20Promoting%20National%2C%20Social%20and%20Environmental%20Values%E2%80%99.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22