n-and-sydney-sweeneys-spider-man-spin-off-opens-to-mixed-critics-reviews%2Farticleshow%2F107681850.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107681850.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E'Madame%20Web'%20opened%20to%20a%20low%2018%25%20score%20on%20Rotten%20Tomatoes.%20While%20some%20critics%20found%20the%20film%20messy%2C%20others%20enjoyed%20its%20fun%20and%20praised%20Dakota%20Johnson's%20performance.%20Fans%20are%20eager%20to%20judge%20the%20movie%20for%20themselves%2C%20noting%20that%20previous%20low-rated%20films%20like%20'Morbius'%20and%20'Venom'%20went%20on%20to%20become%20successful%20franchises.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Hamas%20Commander%20Who%20Orchestrated%20October%207%20Attack%20Spotted%20In%20Tunnel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20released%20footage%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20claiming%20to%20have%20identified%20Hamas%20leader%20Yahya%20Sinwar%20walking%20through%20a%20Gaza%20tunnel%20with%20his%20family%20members.%20If%20confirmed%2C%20this%20marks%20the%20first%20sighting%20of%20Sinwar%20since%20he%20went%20into%20hiding%20ahead%20of%20Hamas's%20October%207%20onslaught%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20IDF%2C%20the%20one-minute-long%20clip%20shows%20Sinwar%20in%20a%20tunnel%20beneath%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20city%20of%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20accompanied%20by%20his%20wife%20and%20three%20children%2C%20led%20by%20his%20brother%20Ibrahim.%20Despite%20his%20back%20facing%20the%20camera%2C%20the%20IDF%20claims%20to%20have%20identified%20Sinwar%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20noting%20distinctive%20features%2C%20such%20as%20the%20size%20of%20the%20figure's%20ears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20