med%20that%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Israeli%20troops%20detained%20close%20relatives%20of%20senior%20Hamas%20military%20commanders%2C%20including%20Sinwar.%20Among%20those%20detained%20were%20the%20father%20of%20Rafa'a%20Salameh%2C%20the%20commander%20of%20Hamas's%20Rafah%20Brigade%2C%20and%20the%20son%20of%20Husni%20Hamdan%2C%20another%20senior%20Hamas%20commander.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IDF%20conducted%20raids%20in%20the%20tunnel%20network%20seen%20in%20the%20October%2010%20footage%2C%20situated%20under%20a%20cemetery%20in%20the%20Bani%20Suheila%20area%20of%20Khan%20Younis.%20According%20to%20Hagari%2C%20the%20tunnels%20contained%20bedrooms%20of%20senior%20Hamas%20officials%20and%20the%20office%20of%20the%20commander%20of%20the%20Khan%20Younis%20Brigade's%20Eastern%20Battalion%2C%20who%20directed%20the%20October%207%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707896160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fpo353vqo_sinwar-_625x300_14_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-gaza-palestine-idf-video-hamas-commander-yahya-sinwar-who-orchestrated-october-7-attack-spotted-in-tunnel-5055275%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20released%20footage%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20claiming%20to%20have%20identified%20Hamas%20leader%20Yahya%20Sinwar%20walking%20through%20a%20Gaza%20tunnel%20with%20his%20family%20members.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-gaza-palestine-idf-video-hamas-commander-yahya-sinwar-who-orchestrated-october-7-attack-spotted-in-tunnel-5055275%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-gaza-palestine-idf-video-hamas-commander-yahya-sinwar-who-orchestrated-october-7-attack-spotted-in-tunnel-5055275%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisra