ng%20a%20law%20to%20guarantee%20MSP%20if%20it%20returns%20to%20power%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20that%20Congress%20was%20not%20in%20the%20government.%20They%20were%20there%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20do%20it.%20They%20have%20a%20habit%20of%20making%20false%20promise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20farmers%20are%20marching%20to%20the%20national%20capital%20in%20a%20mega%20protest.%20They%20are%20demanding%20a%20law%20that%20guarantees%20a%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20for%20all%20crops%2C%20a%20debt%20waiver%20and%20a%20pension%20scheme%2C%20among%20other%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20rounds%20of%20meetings%20between%20government%20representatives%20and%20farmer%20leaders%20have%20failed%20to%20find%20a%20way%20out%20of%20the%20impasse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers'%20march%20to%20Delhi%20has%20been%20blocked%20at%20the%20Haryana-Punjab%20border%2C%20with%20security%20forces%20in%20no%20mood%20to%20let%20them%20pass.%20Delhi%20Police%20have%20imposed%20prohibitory%20orders%20for%20a%20month%20and%20cement%20barriers%2C%20tyre%20deflators%20and%20sandbags%20have%20been%20deployed%20to%20stop%20the%20farmers'%20march.%20Yesterday%2C%20security%20personnel%20used%20tear%20gas%20shells%20and%20water%20cannons%20against%20the%20farmers%2C%20leading%20to%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmer%20leader%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher%20told%20the%20media%20today%20that%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20paramilitary%20forces%20have%20been%20used%20against%20farmers.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20using%20tear%20gas%2C%20rubber%20bullets.%20The%20government%20should%20accept%20our%20demands%20or%20let%20us%20protest.%20This%20is%20our%20democratic%20right.%20Our%20agitation%20is%20peaceful%20and%20we%20will%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707896160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fchcqmg0g_farmers-protest_625x300_14_February_24.jp