nes%20wish%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707894297000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107683343%2Cimgsize-30244.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkareena-kapoor-khan-reveals-saif-ali-khans-epic-reaction-as-she-wished-him-happy-valentines-day%2Farticleshow%2F107683359.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107683359.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%20talks%20about%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan's%20epic%20reaction%20on%20Valentine's%20Day%20and%20it's%20too%20adorable%20and%20real%20to%20miss!%20The%20actors%20have%20hinted%20at%20working%20together%20again%20soon%20and%20it's%20a%20film%20which%20takes%20into%20consideration%20that%20they're%20married!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Husband%20Giving%20Time%2C%20Money%20To%20Mother%20Not%20Domestic%20Violence%3A%20Court%20To%20Woman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20sessions%20court%20in%20Mumbai%20has%20dismissed%20a%20plea%20of%20a%20woman%20challenging%20a%20magistrate%20court%20order%20over%20her%20complaint%20against%20her%20husband%20and%20in-laws%2C%20observing%20that%20a%20man%20giving%20time%20and%20money%20to%20his%20mother%20cannot%20be%20considered%20as%20domestic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20sessions%20judge%20(Dindoshi%20court)%20Ashish%20Ayachit%2C%20in%20the%20order%20passed%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20also%20said%20the%20allegations%20against%20the%20respondents%20are%20vague%20and%20ambiguous%20and%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20prove%20that%20they%20subjected%20the%20applicant%20(woman)%20to%20domestic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%2C%20who%20works%20as%20an%20assistant%20in%20the%20'Mantralaya'%20(state%20secretariat)%2C%20had%20filed%20a%20complaint%20before%20a%20magistrate%20court%20under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Women%20from%20Domestic%20Violence%20Act%20for%20an%20order%20seeking%20protection%2C%20monetary%20relief%20and%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20alleged%20that%20her%20husband%20got%20married%20to%20her%20by%20suppressing%20the%20mental%20illness%20of%20his%20mother%20and%20deceived%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20also%20claimed%20her%20mother-in-law%20opposed%20her%20job%20and%20used%20to%20harass%20her%20and%20that%20her%20husband%20and%20his%20mother%20quarrelled%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20her%20husband%20stayed%20abroad%20for%20his%20job%20from%20September%201993%20to%20December%202004.%20Whenever%20he%20came%20to%20India%20on%20leave%2C%20he%20used%20to%20visit%20his%20mother%20and%20send%20her%20Rs%2010%2C000%20every%20year.%20He%20also%20spent%20money%20for%20his%20mother's%20eye%20operation%2C%20the%20woman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20claimed%20harassment%20by%20the%20other%20members%20of%20her%20in-laws'%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20in-laws%2C%20however%2C%20denied%20all%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20claimed%20that%20she%20never%20accepted%20him%20as%20her%20husband%20and%20used%20to%20level%20false%20allegations%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20he%20had%20filed%20a%20divorce%20petition%20before%20a%20family%20court%20due%20to%20her%20cruelties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20alleged%20that%20his%20wife%20had%20withdrawn%20Rs%2021.68%20lakh%20from%20his%20NRE%20(non-resident%20external)%20account%20without%20any%20information%20and%20purchased%20a%20flat%20with%20the%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pendency%20of%20the%20woman's%20plea%2C%20the%20trial%20court%20(magistrate)%20granted%20her%20an%20interim%20maintenance%20of%20Rs%203%2C000%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20recording%20of%20evidence%20of%20the%20woman%20and%20others%2C%20the%20magistrate%20court%20dismissed%20her%20plea%20and%20vacated%20the%20interim%20directions%20and%20reliefs%20granted%20to%20her%20during%20the%20pendency%20of%20the%20proceeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20subsequently%20filed%20a%20criminal%20appeal%20before%20the%20sessions%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20perusal%20of%20the%20evidence%2C%20the%20sessions%20court%20held%20that%20the%20allegations%20against%20the%20respondents%20are%20%26quot%3Bvague%20and%20ambiguous%26quot%3B%20and%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20prove%20that%20they%20subjected%20the%20woman%20to%20domestic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20record%20that%20the%20applicant%20is%20an%20'assistant'%20working%20in%20Mantralaya%20and%20getting%20a%20salary.%20It%20is%20revealed%20from%20the%20entire%20evidence%20that%20her%20grievance%20is%20that%2C%20the%20respondent%2C%20her%20husband%2C%20is%20giving%20time%20and%20money%20to%20his%20mother%2C%20which%20cannot%20be%20considered%20as%20domestic%20violence%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCareful%20reading%20of%20the%20entire%20evidence%20of%20the%20applicant%20and%20respondent%20number%201(husband)%2C%20I%20am%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20the%20applicant%20has%20miserably%20failed%20to%20prove%20that%20she%20was%20subjected%20to%20domestic%20violence%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20held%20that%20this%20proceeding%20has%20been%20initiated%20only%20after%20the%20issuance%20of%20a%20notice%20by%20the%20woman's%20husband%20for%20seeking%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20was%20not%20entitled%20for%20any%20relief%20under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Women%20from%20Domestic%20Violence%20Act%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20further%20said%20the%20argument%20that%20the%20woman's%20daughter%20is%20unmarried%20and%20therefore%20maintenance%20may%20be%20awarded%20to%20the%20latter%20cannot%20be%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%20I%20do%20not%20think%20that%20the%20applicant%20is%20entitled%20to%20recover%20maintenance%20for%20major%20daughter%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20has%20an%20independent%20remedy%20available%20as%20per%20provisions%20of%20the%20law%2C%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impugned%20judgment%20of%20the%20trial%20court%20does%20not%20require%20interference%20by%20the%20hands%20of%20this%20court%2C%20the%20judge%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707894000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fmpojkr1k_court-generic-fourt-files-generic-files-in-court-pixabay_625x300_11_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhusband-giving-time-money-to-mother-is-not-domestic-violence-court-to-woman-5054870%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20sessions%20court%20in%20Mumbai%20has%20dismissed%20a%20plea%20of%20a%20woman%20over%20her%20complaint%20against%20her%20husband%20and%20in-laws%2C%20observing%20that%20a%20man%20giving%20time%20and%20money%20to%20his%20mother%20cannot%20be%20considered%20domestic%20violence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhusband-giving-time-money-to-mother-is-not-domestic-violence-court-to-woman-5054870%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhusband-giving-time-money-to-mother-is-not-domestic-violence-court-to-woman-5054870%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhusband-giving-time-money-to-mother-is-not-domestic-violence-court-to-woman-5054870%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20is%20playing%20what%20in%20Rohit%20Shetty's%20co