y%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchandigarh%2Fwhy-block-roads-when-farmers-have-right-to-assembly-movement-high-court%2Farticleshow%2F107670598.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20of%20acting%20Chief%20Justice%20G.S.%20Sandhawalia%20and%20Justice%20Lapita%20Banerji%20considered%20the%20public%20interest%20litigation%20by%20Panchkula%20lawyer%20Uday%20Pratap%20Singh%20against%20the%20sealing%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20borders%20%E2%80%93%20photos%20of%20which%20have%20flooded%20social%20media.%20Police%20have%20put%20up%20barricades%20made%20of%20cement%2C%20installed%20spikes%20and%20placed%20layers%20of%20obstacles%20on%20the%20road%20to%20prevent%20farmers%20from%20reaching%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%20144%20has%20been%20imposed%20in%20some%20areas%2C%20banning%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20impleaded%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20asked%20for%20responses%20from%20the%20Haryana%2C%20Punjab%20and%20Chandigarh%20governments%20and%20administration%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%E2%80%99%20organisations%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20and%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20who%20are%20leading%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20expedition%20have%20also%20been%20impleaded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20districts%20where%20there%20is%20no%20internet%20in%20Haryana%20are%20Ambala%2C%20Kurukshetra%2C%20Kaithal%2C%20Jind%2C%20Hisar%2C%20Fatehabad%20and%20Sirsa%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fharyana%2Ffarmers-protest-haryana-extends-suspension-of-internet-services-till-feb-15-2893362%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported%3Cem%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3EInternet%20will%20be%20off%20in%20these%20areas%20till%20February%2015%2C%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20a%20reliable%20medium%20to%20an%20opaque%20one%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawyer%20and%20former%20head%20of%20the%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%20has%20noted%20on%20X%20as%20to%20how%20%E2%80%9Ctimely%20and%20reliable%E2%80%9D%20a%20medium%20the%20site%20was%20for%20the%20first%20chapter%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20in%202020-2021.%20Then%2C%20it%20was%20called%20Twitter%20and%20was%20run%20by%20Jack%20Dorsey.%20In%20October%202022%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20purchased%20Twitter%2C%20which%20was%20renamed%20and%20began%20to%20adhere%20to%20policies%20aimed%20at%20appeasing%20local%20laws%20%E2%80%93%20even%20if%20it%20infringed%20upon%20the%20freedom%20of%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ETwitter%20was%20a%20reliable%20and%20timely%20medium%20for%20farmers%20during%20their%20protests%20in%202020-21.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20issued%20official%20press%20releases%2C%20documented%20police%20excesses%2C%20built%20community%20and%20sympathy%20for%20their%20cause%20with%20hashtags.%20It%20became%20a%20vital%20informational%20pipeline%20for%20farmers%20to%20convey%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Apar%20(%40apar1984)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fapar1984%2Fstatus%2F1757431828124995804%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2013%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CThey%20issued%20official%20press%20releases%2C%20documented%20police%20excesses%2C%20built%20community%20and%20sympathy%20for%20their%20cause%20with%20hashtags.%20It%20became%20a%20vital%20informational%20pipeline%20for%20farmers%20to%20convey%20their%20demands%20and%20debunk%20disinformation%20when%20the%20TV%20broadcast%20and%20news%20networks%20are%20clearly%20partisan%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Union%20Government.%20All%20of%20this%20is%20a%20legal%20democratic%20right%20in%20a%20country%20with%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20speech%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gupta%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20today%20is%20different%2C%20he%20added%2C%20noting%20that%20blocking%20orders%20for%20X%20accounts%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20leaders%20had%20clearly%20been%20issued%20in%20advance.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20form%20of%20pre-censorship%20is%20without%20any%20transparency%20or%20natural%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGupta%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20under%20the%20new%20ownership%2C%20the%20site%20no%20longer%20discloses%20withheld%20URLs%20to%20the%20Lumen%20Database%2C%20thus%20taking%20away%20any%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGupta%20adds%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20on%20its%20part%20will%20not%20disclose%20or%20submit%20to%20accountability.%20Why%20block%20entire%20accounts%20in%20advance%3F%20Is%20the%20account%20itself%20illegal%3F%20It%20will%20not%20bother%20asking%20these%20questions%20for%20fewer%20people%20will%20ask%20them%20today%20than%20two%20years%20ago.%20As%20its%20march%20towards%20total%20power%20becomes%20menacing%20it%20commands%20greater%20levels%20of%20social%20compliance.%20Either%20by%20discipline%2C%20despondency%20or%20indoctrination.%20This%20is%20not%20surprising%2C%20what%20does%20provide%20anguish%20is%20the%20vile%20commentary%20against%20farmers%20on%20social%20media.%20How%20easy%20it%20is%20to%20forget%20that%20close%20to%20750%20protestors%20who%20lost%20their%20lives%3F%20Have%20we%20as%20a%20society%20lost%20all%20civility%20in%20disagreement%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707889527000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14105336%2FScreenshot-2024-02-14-at-10.53.23%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-internet-haryana-twitter-accounts%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court%20has%20asked%20why%20farmers%20should%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20move%20through%20a%20National%20Highway%20seeing%20that%20they%20had%20the%20right%20to%2