0family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20had%20a%20gun%2C%20and%20I%20heard%20they%20one%20of%20them%20has%20also%20committed%20a%20murder%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20didn't%20tell%20anyone.%20When%20the%20video%20went%20viral%2C%20I%20informed%20my%20elder%20brother%20that%20this%20had%20happened%20to%20me%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20and%20hunt%20is%20on%20for%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20distressing%20event%20follows%20another%20incident%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Betul%20recently%2C%20where%20another%20tribal%20man%20was%20beaten%20brutally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20a%20tribal%20man%20was%20assaulted%20and%20made%20to%20pose%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmurga%26quot%3B%20in%20Betul.%20The%20victim%20was%20subjected%20to%20physical%20violence%20and%20casteist%20slurs%20by%20a%20group%20led%20by%20Chanchal%20Rajput%2C%20an%20alleged%20member%20of%20Bajrang%20Dal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaju%2C%20who%20works%20as%20a%20DJ%2C%20narrated%20the%20harrowing%20experience%3A%20%26quot%3BAt%20around%2011%3A30%20pm%2C%20while%20I%20was%20on%20my%20way%20home%2C%20I%20was%20picked%20up%20near%20Subhash%20School%20by%20Chanchal%20Rajput%20and%20his%20Bajrang%20Dal%20friends.%20They%20assaulted%20me%20physically%20and%20verbally%2C%20and%20used%20casteist%20slurs%20against%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficial%20statistics%20though%20suggest%20a%20decrease%20in%20serious%20crimes%20against%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20in%20the%20state.%20According%20to%20data%20released%20by%20the%20Ajak%20branch%20of%20the%20police%20headquarters%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%2022%25%20reduction%20in%20severe%20crimes%20against%20these%20communities%20from%202022%20to%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20there%20were%2011%2C384%20reported%20cases%20of%20crimes%20against%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20while%20in%202023%2C%20the