20%3Cp%3EChristopher%20Polk%2FBillboard%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EO'Neal%20launched%20Shaq's%20Fun%20House%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0described%20as%20%26quot%3Bpart%20carnival%2C%20part%20music%20festival%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20edition%20was%20held%20at%20XS%20nightclub%20in%20the%20Wynn%20Las%20Vegas%20hotel%20on%20Friday%20and%20featured%20performances%20from%20Lil%20Wayne%2C%20Diplo%2C%20and%20O'Neal%20himself%20(aka%20DJ%20Diesel).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20stars%20came%20out%20in%20full%20force%20to%20party%20with%20the%20NBA%20legend.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DJ%20Irie%2C%20Flavor%20Flav.%20and%20Shaquille%20O'Neal%20%26quot%3BDJ%20Diesel%26quot%3B%20at%20Shaq's%20Fun%20House%202024%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cabce46fcb546d2d4edd8d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221332%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDJ%20Irie%2C%20Flavor%20Flav%2C%20and%20Shaquille%20O'Neal%20at%20Shaq's%20Fun%20House%202024.%20%3Cp%3EChristopher%20Polk%2FBillboard%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20celebrities%20at%20Shaq's%20Fun%20House%20were%20Ciara%20and%20Russell%20Wilson%2C%20Guy%20Fieri%2C%20Nick%20and%20Vanessa%20Lachey%2C%20Casey%20Affleck%2C%20Flavor%20Flav%2C%20Fat%20Joe%2C%20and%20the%20Chainsmokers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20only%20the%20VIP%20party%20was%20being%20held%20indoors.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shaq's%20Fun%20House%202024%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65caca6694aa8ee8e84a79cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELil%20Wayne%20performing%20at%20Shaq's%20Fun%20House.%20%3Cp%3EMedium%20Rare%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EXS%20is%20over%2040%2C000%20square%20feet%20and%20has%20both%20a%20massive%20indoor%