her%20arms%2C%20legs%2C%20and%20head%20into%20the%20center%20of%20her%20body.%20The%20same%20thing%20happens%20with%20the%20polar%20vortex.%20When%20it%20spins%20fast%2C%20the%20cold%20air%20stays%20tucked%20close%20to%20the%20center%20of%20rotation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20when%20the%20polar%20vortex%20slows%20down%2C%20its%20grip%20on%20this%20cold%20air%20loosens.%20This%20is%20what%20triggers%20Arctic%20outbreaks%20like%20Lorraine%3A%20when%20cold%20air%20in%20the%20polar%20jet%20stream%20surges%20down%20to%20lower%20latitudes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20loosening%20and%20tightening%20of%20this%20grip%20is%20normal.%20The%20polar%20vortex%20tends%20to%20weaken%20in%20the%20summer%20and%20strengthen%20in%20the%20winter.%20But%20climate%20change%20is%20disrupting%20this%20cycle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20that%20climate%20change%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20Arctic%20is%20favoring%20this%20weak%20polar%20vortex%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20Cohen%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20you%20get%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20probability%20of%20severe%20winter%20weather%2C%20cold%2C%20or%20snowfall.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWinter%20storm%20Lorraine%20is%20a%20direct%20result%20of%20this%20phenomenon.%20Last%20week%2C%20the%20polar%20vortex%20was%20strong%20and%20tight.%20But%20this%20week%2C%20it%20stretched%20out%20like%20a%20rubber%20band%2C%20Cohen%20said%2C%20sending%20a%20blast%20of%20cold%20temperatures%20and%20snowfall%20to%20the%20East%20Coast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3EArctic%20warming%20is%20disrupting%20the%20polar%20vortex%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Death%20Valley%20in%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a7bdf46075be0019c2eede%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDeath%20Valley%20in%20California%20last