rs%20immediate%20application%20feasibility%20for%20municipal%20corporations%2C%20industries%2C%20sewage%20treatment%20facilities%2C%20aquatic%20weeds%20and%20various%20organic%20waste%20management%20sectors.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20scaled-up%20process%20successfully%20produced%20100%20to%20150%20kg%20of%20vermicompost%20within%20a%20month%20from%20250%20to%20300%20kg%20of%20daily%20waste%20fed.%20The%20increased%20earthworm%20count%20resulted%20in%20the%20secondary%20end%20product%20being%20the%20earthworm%20itself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20he%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20study%20included%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332396%2Fhow-to-make-bio-enzymes-from-kitchen-waste-at-home-diy-steps-by-kolkata-gardener-nita-singh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evegetable%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20aquatic%20weed%20(water%20hyacinth)%20as%20prime%20substrates%2C%20both%20in%20mono-substrate%20composting%20and%20co-composting.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20entire%20study%2C%20we%20have%20converted%2015%20tonnes%20of%20waste%20collected%20from%20the%20markets%20and%20ponds%20around%20the%20IIT%20Guwahati%20campus%20(350%20kg%20per%20day).%20The%20confidence%20that%20we%20gained%20through%20the%20study%20is%20the%20basis%20on%20which%20we%20are%20suggesting%20that%20the%20technology%20can%20handle%20sizable%20quantities.%20We%20believe%20this%20process%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20reshape%20organic%20waste%20treatment%20facilities%20globally%2C%20providing%20an%20environmentally%20compatible%20solution%20to%20mitigate%20contamination%20hazards%20and%20produce%20an%20outstanding%20soil%20conditioner%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20IIT-Guwahati)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707746351000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341515%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Ajay%20S%20Kalamdhad%20led%20a%20group%20of%20IIT-Guwahati%20researchers%20to%20innovate%20a%20two-stage%20fast%20biodegradation%20technique%20that%20can%20aid%20municipal%20corporations%20in%20eco-friendly%20organic%20waste%20management.%20It%20also%20produces%20%E2%80%98Mati%20Dhan%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20top-notch%20vermicompost%20and%20organic%20compost%20rich%20in%20NPK%20and%20other%20essential%20nutrients%20for%20farmers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%227%20Best%20Dosa%20Places%20in%20Chennai%20That%20Also%20Serve%20Epic%20South%20Indian%20Thalis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20map%20of%20decadent%20fine-dining%20restaurants%20on%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%20bustling%20streets%20is%20interspersed%20with%20traditional%20hole-in-the-wall%20eateries.%20These%20usually%20cater%20to%20two%20palates%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20delights%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333205%2Fprasanna-karthik-viral-tweet-idli-in-tadka-restaurant-in-japan-for-south-indian-breakfast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESouth%20Indian%20breakfasts%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20other%20that%20takes%20pleasure%20in%20meaty%20main%20courses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vibrant%20city%20takes%20great%20pride%20in%20its%20gastronomy%20and%20has%20enjoyed%20breathless%20coverage%20of%20its%20military-era%20hotels.%20And%20history%20lets%20us%20in%20on%20their%20inception.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20goes%20that%20it%20was%20during%20World%20War%20II%20that%20these%20military%20outlets%20mushroomed%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20satisfy%20the%20troops%E2%80%99%20hunger.%20Now%2C%20neither%20the%20emergence%20of%20t