niture-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einto%20furniture%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20not%20many%20have%20fully%20harnessed%20the%20material%E2%80%99s%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20plant%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Professor%20Ankit%20Kumar%20Changawala%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CBamboo%20is%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkit%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20individuals%20who%20have%20made%20efforts%20to%20utilise%20the%20material%20to%20its%20fullest%20extent%2C%20recently%20obtaining%20a%20patent%20for%20a%20bamboo%20chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20chair%20is%20sturdy%2C%20strong%2C%20and%20can%20last%20up%20to%2020%20years.%20It%20is%20the%20first%20bamboo%20chair%20to%20be%20patented%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESustainability%20meets%20design%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20in%20Surat%2C%20Ankit%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20pursue%20design%2C%20but%20he%20lacked%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20pursuing%20a%20diploma%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Fthis-single-mother-broke-some-big-barriers-to-become-indias-1st-woman-engineer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecivil%20engineering%2C%20t%3C%2Fa%3Ehinking%20it%20might%20help%20me%20in%20designing%20things.%20However%2C%20during%20the%20course%2C%20I%20realised%20it%20was%20not%20something%20I%20wanted%20to%20pursue.%20It%20was%20my%20professor%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20an%20interior%20designer%2C%20whose%20work%20inspired%20me%20and%20made%20me%20realise%20my%20true%20passion%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ankit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConfused%20about%20how%20to%20pursue%20his%20interest%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20enrol%20in%20an%20interior%20design%20course%20at%20Veer%20Narmad%20South%20Gujarat%20University%20(VNSGU).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20he%20serves%20as%20an%20assistant%20professor%20at%20the%20same%20university.%20%E2%80%9CTeaching%20made%20me%20realise%20how%20much%20I%20enjoy%20it.%20I%20found%20my%20true%20calling%20in%20both%20designing%20and%20educating%20students%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-6-1707399873.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20first%20patented%20bamboo%20chair%20made%20by%20Professor%20Ankit%20Kumar%20Changawala%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-6-1707399873.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-6-1707399873-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-6-1707399873-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-6-1707399873-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-6-1707399873-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341209%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20patented%20bamboo%20chair%20was%20made%20by%20Professor%20Ankit%20Kumar%20Changawala%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339622%2Frare-species-of-bamboo-in-kerala-india-farming-for-sustainable-future-desertification%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintroduction%20to%20bamboo%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20his%20idea%20of%20a%20bamboo%20chair%2C%20he%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20given%20the%20opportunity%20to%20attend%20a%20workshop%20in%202019%20in%20Manipur.%20The%20World%20Bamboo%20Workshop%20was%20the%20first%20symposium%20in%20India%20focused%20on%20bamboo%20and%20its%20uses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20symposium%20profoundly%20changed%20Ankit%E2%80%99s%20perception%20of%20bamboo.%20Previously%2C%20there%20was%20merely%20abundant%20vegetation%20in%20the%20region.%20%E2%80%9CI%20could%20see%20its%20untapped%20potential%20and%20how%20it%20was%20being%20wasted.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20discovered%20a%20community%20of%20bamboo%20artisans%20whose%20craft%20was%20fading%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Kotwaliyas%20in%20the%20region%20are%20renowned%20for%20their%20skill%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20their%20art%20was%20being%20neglected%20and%20dying%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkit%20also%20began%20educating%20his%20students%20about%20the%20benefits%20of%20using%20Bambusa%20bamboo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20was%20in%20the%20process%20of%20educating%20more%20people%20and%20reaching%20out%20to%20craftsmen%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20disrupting%20everything%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20period%2C%20Ankit%20encountered%20craftsmen%20suffering%20due%20to%20the%20decline%20in%20tourism.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learned%20that%20the%20younger%20generations%20of%20these%20craftsmen%20were%20reluctant%20to%20continue%20the%20tradition%20as%20they%20saw%20no%20future%20in%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Ankit%2C%20demonstrating%20the%20immense%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334214%2Fmaharashtra-tetwali-village-namita-namdev-bhurkood-bamboo-kandils-trains-tribal-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epotential%20of%20bamboo%3C%2Fa%3E%20became%20crucial.%20%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20them%20to%20abandon%20their%20craft%20and%20migrate%20to%20cities%20in%20search%20of%20jobs.%20So%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20create%20daily-use%20furniture%20with%20modern%20designs%20to%20appeal%20to%20urban%20consumers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Ankit%2C%20along%20with%20a%20few%20students%20and%20four%20local%20craftsmen%2C%20embarked%20on%20creating%20sustainable%20yet%20modern%20designs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESturdy%2C%20Sustainable%20and%20Modern%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20step%20for%20Ankit%20was%20to%20understand%20the%20bamboo.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20designers%2C%20we%20work%20with%20measurements%20but%20these%20traditional%20craftsmen%20have%20their%20own%20way%20of%20working.%20We%20realised%20how%20the%20wood%20in%20bamboo%20towards%20the%20lower%20end%20was%20stronger%20and%20thicker%20than%20the%20upper%20end%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-7-1707399921.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22It%20took%20almost%20two%20years%20for%20Ankit%20to%20design%20and%20built%20the%20chair.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-7-1707399921.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-7-1707399921-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-7-1707399921-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-7-1707399921-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-7-1707399921-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341210%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20took%20almost%20two%20years%20for%20Ankit%20to%20design%20and%20build%20the%20chair.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20the%20craftsmen%20comfortable%20and%20win%20their%20confidence%2C%20Ankit%20took%20his%20designs%20to%20their%20workshops.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20make%20them%20feel%20comfortable%20and%20work%20as%20a%20team.%20They%20were%20at%20their%20best%20form%20when%20they%20were%20using%20their%20own%20traditional%20machines%20and%20materials.%20I%20used%20to%20visit%20their%20workshops%20in%20order%20to%20work%20on%20the%20chair%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20Bambusa%20bamboo%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20chose%20Bambusa%20because%20it%20has%20a%20great%20load-bearing%20capacity.%20It%20is%20long-lasting%20and%20sturdy%20enough%20to%20be%20used%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20The%20knots%20in%20the%20variety%20are%20very%20close%20making%20it%20very%20strong.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20variety%20is%20also%20abundantly%20available%20in%20the%20area.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20companies%20making%20furniture%20from%20bamboo%20imported%20from%20different%20countries.%20If%20you%20go%20online%20and%20try%20to%20find%20a%20simple%20piece%20of%20furniture%20made%20out%20of%20bamboo%2C%20it%20will%20be%20quite%20expensive.%20The%20reason%20is%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20because%20they%20are%20not%20using%20Indian%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkit%20adds%20that%20he%20used%20a%20native%20variety%20because%20he%20wanted%20to%20keep%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20chair%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331893%2Fmental-health-care-therapy-counselling-affordable-startups-india-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaffordable%20and%20cheap.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20point%20in%20making%20a%20product%20that%20the%20masses%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford.%20It%20defeats%20the%20entire%20sustainability%20angle%20behind%20the%20product%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CGujarat%20government%20has%20also%20released%20a%20lot%20of%20schemes%20for%20the%20farmers%20to%20encourage%20them%20to%20grow%20the%20plant%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20cost%20of%20funding%20the%20project%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20it%20out%20of%20my%20own%20pocket.%20I%20knew%20if%20I%20had%20gone%20out%20looking%20for%20funding%20then%20this%20would%20not%20have%20happened.%20Investors%20would%20lack%20confidence%20in%20the%20idea%20since%20it%20was%20new%20back%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Ankit%20nearly%20two%20years%20to%20complete%20the%20design%20and%20make%20the%20chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202023%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20ahead%20and%20get%20the%20chair%20patented.%20The%20main%20reason%20behind%20it%20was%20to%20showcase%20the%20potential%20of%20native%20bamboo%20species%20to%20the%20world.%20Once%20my%20design%20got%20patented%2C%20it%20generated%20a%20conversation%20among%20people%20about%20the%20potential%20of%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20chair%20can%20endure%20150%20kgs%20of%20weight%20and%20can%20last%20more%20than%2020%20years.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20clas